snippet.title: 11. TastyCups #4 Grand Finals: Necrophag1st vs Proteh
snippet.description:
The last game of the stream, the grand final between these two titans of the game.

The TastyCup Doom Edition #4 took place on February 2nd 2019, organized by Jehar and broadcasted on https://www.twitch.tv/tastyspleentv

Sixteen players participated in a double elimination bracket to determine the best QC:DE player. Cash prize pool started at $100 and would increase based on donations.

-------------------------------------
Get the current version of QCDE (2.7) here:
http://www.moddb.com/mods/quake-champions-doom-edition

(the tastycup was played on v2.2, but that's super outdated now)

-------------------------------------
Music by Michael Markie, part of the QCDE OST

You can acquire the original tracks from the OST here:
https://markiemusic.bandcamp.com/album/augmented


-------------------------------------
Join our discord where we announce when we're playing, and all sorts of stuff.
https://discord.gg/RN9hhmA

-------------------------------------
DBT's Twitch channel where QCDE is streamed on the regular
https://www.twitch.tv/dbthanatos/
